    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>Jumping word-wise in the iTerm2 (3.0 beta):</p>

<ul>
<li>Open the Preferences Pane</li>
<li>Goto Tab Keys</li>
<li>Create a new Key Binding with the Shortcut “⌥ + ←” and use “Send Escape Sequence” as the Action and Set “Esc + b”</li>
<li>Create a new Key Binding with the Shortcut “⌥ + →” and use “Send Escape Sequence” as the Action and Set “Esc + f”</li>
</ul>


<p><img src="/images/iterm-jump-words.png" alt="iTerm Jump/Tab Words" /></p>
